{"tid":1640902,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"除左網購... 仲有冇其他Project可以幫到義士","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:12:21.000Z","uid":58805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0b26a30f21d08b4376b62a8d9986ccf69740f52a","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"而家見到有光時project，大家都好熱心幫手，希望將來義士會多D支援<br />\n但係我比較悲觀，呢類要靠大家長時間support既Project，當社會平靜返我好擔心Sustain唔到，同埋都想討論下除左光時網購，有冇其他可行Project 都可以一齊進行，想各位都Brain Storm一下。我係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">前提: </span></strong><br />\n香港人其實好善忘，局勢動蕩非常時期大家好記得落力支援義士，但當一切塵埃落定生活慢慢回歸平淡，好現實地相信會有一部份人忘記左呢份熱情，如果一個要靠大量人長時間支持既Project (例如網店，貨物數量比外面少，價錢較貴，會唔會愈來愈少人記得去買？)，可持續性有危機<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現時優勢:</span></strong><br />\n同路人即時集資能力好強，如果個Project大家覺得行得通，眾籌出一千幾百萬係好簡單既事<br />\n<br />\n所以我想講... 除左光時Project，有冇可能做到一個只需要集資一次，靠幾個有心人run起個頭，之後唔需要長時間靠人支援，都可以一直幫到義士架呢？暫時想法有兩個︰<br />\n<br />\n1. 支援義士做個體戶過渡<br />\n集資開展一個「租車生意」，買入二手車，資助義士考車牌，成本價租車做Uber、貨Van<br />\n好處: 個體戶時間自由，義士可以選擇用黎做正職，亦可以用黎做搵到自己想做既工作前既過渡<br />\n壞處: Uber犯法、唔係個個義士想學車<br />\n<br />\n2. 黃色JobsDB<br />\n其實好多公司/僱主唔介意請有案底義士，不過冇渠道公開講，如果整個黃色JobsDB，所有有人力需求、又唔介意請義士既，都可以將職位登上去，然後義士睇呢個請人網站就起碼知道對方應該係同路人，請人方應可以優先考慮呢個平台交過黎既submission。<br />\n好處: 成本好低，只要有IT人而家都可以做, 唔駛集資<br />\n壞處: 唔知會唔會有鬼搞事<br />\n<br />\n呢個係我少少想法，想大家都一齊討論下仲有咩可能性，盡量抗大日後對義士可以做到既支援，好冇？"},{"pid":"4fbaefaec6398ae7a88bc50a19ecbaf603b0aac9","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"全港最黃嘅光時網物平台於10月7日上線啦!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629141</a>"},{"pid":"f80ccd96e05ec8670afbed2922bd2a090af7e013","tid":1640902,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d085c938f9de5ab8c492a8aaf523dd65e505a9b5","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a48ac3544e555c416a9c2c6e349690274cca7539","tid":1640902,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"497c0c19bfb910e37fdfd00742ddbf15f8e681cc","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"[內附日程表] 你地休息完未？肯做野未？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640548</a>"},{"pid":"1fe44a3666c61ff4ce2ff333864a9d2affa7de21","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"965dd79d190d240f16528e0323062b639cda701a","tid":1640902,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"幫你手推"},{"pid":"07020fafee51e180de656767834deedd103dc63c","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"求其他手足意見"},{"pid":"a47f3b204f42692ac2b078841e8e77cd15711ef7","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"黃色Job Matching Platform 有冇IT人可以幫手做啊~"},{"pid":"b3ee9574c2e10245786fffcd93222390a4452802","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"adeab271d40bd2c56cf305df53dca04f335e6342","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起 T_T"},{"pid":"c7eddbac7844bec41ca76b7a8ad426095ef0f75a","tid":1640902,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"⚙️黨鐵個人資料保障⚙️<br />\n友頻 <a href=\"https://t.me/securehk/224\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsecurehk%2F224&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=76956400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/securehk/224</a> 提到，根據#MTRapp份使用條款 End-User agreement, 個app本身隨時可以靜靜雞偷取你O既電話資料及收集行蹤。<br />\n同埋，如果你用#VPN O既話，而家直頭係load 唔到個app添！<br />\n大家睇下呢條片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1tRg0Tx1ukU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1tRg0Tx1ukU&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=98832df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1tRg0Tx1ukU</a><br />\n咁點算? <br />\n⚠️Android去 設定&gt;應用程式權限&gt;閂晒關於#黨鐵app O既所有權限⚠️<br />\n⚠️iOS去 Settings &gt;Apps &gt; MTR Mobile &gt; Allow MTR Mobile to access⚠️<br />\n閂晒關於黨鐵app O既所有權限<br />\n‼️Source: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKPrivacy‼️\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKPrivacy%E2%80%BC%EF%B8%8F&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=be5d1445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKPrivacy‼️</a>"},{"pid":"328c3edf5bb956c624c72cf46dbad3a7e66be50a","tid":1640902,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ff559c460ca904804791244fa51272d0d8fcae49","tid":1640902,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"878425436c10e926100ef307758a83ce2b49e347","tid":1640902,"uid":204625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1bd83c84dd7ca72da187bba5d5b847b0e3937e28","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:41:13.000Z","msg":"其實最好係可以做過渡性支援<br />\n一來手足各有追求，唔一定要局限左佢地可以做既事，只要o係佢地未做到未支援到自己時比到少少幫忙已經名<br />\n二來我覺得香港始終有好多同路人，就算有案底其實都唔太影響工作，除非特定行業 (金融會計老師之類..)"},{"pid":"ca600d7bf9ff4cbeb920258a4a2034637adf7b99","tid":1640902,"uid":58805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}